high_descs: Turn left and move to the black table.
Pick up the tomato on the black table.
Bring the tomato to the microwave.
Heat the tomato in the microwave.
Bring the tomato out of the microwave and to the left.
Put the heated tomato on the black table, left of the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated tomato on the black table, left of the microwave.

high_descs: turn right to the counter by the refrigerator
grab the tomato on the counter
walk to the right a little
open the microwave, put the tomato in the microwave, heat the tomato, take the tomato out
walk to the left a little
put the tomato back on the counter
anns.task_desc: heat the tomato with microwave, put it back on the counter

high_descs: Turn to the right and face the microwave.
Pick the tomato up from left of the microwave.
Move to the left to face the microwave.
Put the tomato in the microwave and then shut the door and then open the door, take the tomato out and shut the door.
Move to the left and face the left of the microwave.
Set the tomato down left of the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put a warmed tomato down on the cart.

high_descs: Turn right and walk up to the counter with the microwave on it
Pick up the tomato from the counter
Move right slightly then turn back left to face the microwave
Put the tomato in the microwave, cook it, and remove it
Move left slightly then turn right to face back toward the counter
Put the tomato on the counter just left of the microwave
anns.task_desc: Put the cooked tomato on the counter

high_descs: Turn around to the counter behind.
Pick up the tomato from the left side of the counter.
Take the tomato and move a step to the right.
Open the microwave and place the tomato inside and turn it on. Remove the tomato when finished.
Take the tomato and move a step to the left.
Place the tomato back on the counter, towards the back behind the green cup.
anns.task_desc: Heat a tomato and place it on the counter.

high_descs: Turn right and face the counter with the microwave on it.
Pick up the tomato that's in front of the egg.
Move in front of the microwave to the right.
Open the microwave door, place the tomato inside next to the apple, close the door, heat the tomato, open the microwave door, take the tomato out, and close the door.
Move to the left of the microwave.
Put the tomato on the counter and in front of the egg where it originally was.
